Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.gkelly.engine.Manager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UIManager

    public abstract class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class to be extended to create managers
    Example: One manager for main menu, another for game, then switch between them as needed
